    <arm_group_type>Experimental</arm_group_type>
    <description>-Participants receive low-literacy educational and instructional brochures at the time of fecal occult blood test (FOBT) referral. Participants with a positive FOBT receive a second low-literacy brochure on bowel preparation for colonoscopy and the importance of follow-up, and assist with scheduling and completing colonoscopy</description>
